1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:09,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>This program is suitable
for viewers ages 15 and up.</i></font>

2
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:20,960
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[MY SHY BOSS]</i></font>

3
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:27,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad! The food is ready!</font>

4
00:00:43,150 --> 00:00:45,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. Let's eat.</font>

5
00:00:54,970 --> 00:00:56,630
<font color=#FFFF00>How does it taste?</font>

6
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:00,510
<font color=#FFFF00>It's good.</font>

7
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,970
<font color=#FFFF00>That's a relief.</font>

8
00:01:11,250 --> 00:01:16,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, Dad. I wish you'd start
telling me what you're thinking.</font>

9
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:19,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? I think it's fine.</font>

10
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:21,460
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it's not.</font>

11
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:26,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, I'm going to be late.</font>

12
00:01:35,490 --> 00:01:37,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you planning to
continue working there?</font>

13
00:01:38,650 --> 00:01:43,210
<font color=#FFFF00>You entered that company
with ill intentions...</font>

14
00:01:49,850 --> 00:01:53,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hye was the one who sent me there.</font>

15
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:56,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Buy this for me instead.</font>

16
00:01:56,030 --> 00:01:59,810
<font color=#FFFF00>I have a really important audition
after my last performance.</font>

17
00:01:59,810 --> 00:02:05,590
<font color=#FFFF00>If I wear this, I feel like
they'll acknowledge my worth.</font>

18
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:09,580
<font color=#FFFF00>I found someone who understands me</font>

19
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:15,120
<font color=#FFFF00>and I found a place
that acknowledges my worth.</font>

20
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:18,170
<font color=#FFFF00>And Ji Hye was the one
who made it happen.</font>

21
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:20,190
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what I think.</font>

22
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:25,500
<font color=#FFFF00>But I heard that necklace
wasn't even a gift from Ji Hye.</font>

23
00:02:28,010 --> 00:02:32,210
<font color=#FFFF00>But instead,
I received a prettier necklace.</font>

24
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:45,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Geez, it's blinding me!</font>

25
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:49,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, is that a food tray or a mirror?
It'll burn a hole in the ground.</font>

26
00:02:54,930 --> 00:02:57,100
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

27
00:02:57,100 --> 00:03:01,400
<font color=#FFFF00>I know you're not here to do dishes.
It's because you want to talk, right?</font>

28
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:11,100
<font color=#FFFF00>- Well...
- Tell me.</font>

29
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:16,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't stay all serious
and quiet by yourself.</font>

30
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:19,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you realize how
that makes other people feel?</font>

31
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:23,040
<font color=#FFFF00>- Really?
- Are you really asking me that?</font>

32
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I just want
you to understand me?</font>

33
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,920
<font color=#FFFF00>I want to understand you too.</font>

34
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:31,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop reading into what
everyone else is thinking</font>

35
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:33,350
<font color=#FFFF00>and tell us what you're thinking too.</font>

36
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,540
<font color=#FFFF00>I wasn't reading anyone.</font>

37
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:43,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, I guess I did often
try to go the easy route.</font>

38
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:49,270
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought I could see what everyone
was feeling. That I could read it.</font>

39
00:03:51,530 --> 00:03:53,410
<font color=#FFFF00>But it wasn't true.</font>

40
00:03:53,410 --> 00:03:58,040
<font color=#FFFF00>I deluded myself into thinking
I knew and understood them.</font>

41
00:04:00,230 --> 00:04:02,250
<font color=#FFFF00>But it was dangerous.</font>

42
00:04:03,650 --> 00:04:07,340
<font color=#FFFF00>- What do you mean?
- I'm talking about Secretary Chae.</font>

43
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:11,110
<font color=#FFFF00>It's possible...</font>

44
00:04:11,990 --> 00:04:15,210
<font color=#FFFF00>that it all started because of me.</font>

45
00:05:00,730 --> 00:05:03,140
<font color=#FFFF00>That...</font>

46
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:13,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Boss!</font>

47
00:05:14,310 --> 00:05:18,400
<font color=#FFFF00>I was worried about you.
Where were you all day?</font>

48
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:23,070
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you not to close your doors!
No more secrets.</font>

49
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:27,210
<font color=#FFFF00>It hasn't been long,
but you're being stubborn again.</font>

50
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:34,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Um, Boss.</font>

51
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:40,380
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong? Did something happen?</font>

52
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:45,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Why...</font>

53
00:05:47,550 --> 00:05:52,790
<font color=#FFFF00>are there always more reasons
for why we shouldn't be together?</font>

54
00:05:52,790 --> 00:05:54,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Pardon?</font>

55
00:06:10,490 --> 00:06:18,990
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[EPISODE 15: ONE REASON THAT IS MORE
IMPORTANT THAN 99 OTHER REASONS]</i></font>

56
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:26,130
<font color=#FFFF00>You're CEO Eun Hwan Ki, right?</font>

57
00:06:26,130 --> 00:06:30,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, but who are you?</font>

58
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:32,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

59
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:36,180
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just... Ro Woon's
neighborhood friend.</font>

60
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:37,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh.</font>

61
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:40,180
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

62
00:06:42,020 --> 00:06:47,580
<font color=#FFFF00>It looks like you feel relieved,
thinking that it's all over.</font>

63
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:50,230
<font color=#FFFF00>But what do we do?</font>

64
00:06:50,230 --> 00:06:55,660
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't deserve to
smile next to Chae Ro Woon.</font>

65
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:59,170
<font color=#FFFF00>- You don't.
- Pardon?</font>

66
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:01,540
<font color=#FFFF00>There is something you don't know.</font>

67
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:07,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hye...</font>

68
00:07:09,410 --> 00:07:12,250
<font color=#FFFF00>didn't like Kang Woo Il, but you.</font>

69
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:16,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Um, wait...</font>

70
00:07:17,370 --> 00:07:19,700
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure what you're saying.</font>

71
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:22,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course you had no idea.</font>

72
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:25,730
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure you didn't
give her the time of day.</font>

73
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:28,560
<font color=#FFFF00>I think you're mistaken.</font>

74
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:32,560
<font color=#FFFF00>The way Ji Hye got involved
with Kang Woo Il...</font>

75
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,860
<font color=#FFFF00>is beyond me.</font>

76
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:38,400
<font color=#FFFF00>But that also started because of you.</font>

77
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:44,300
<font color=#FFFF00>She wanted to hear something
from your friend, at the very least.</font>

78
00:08:06,650 --> 00:08:10,650
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Should I ask CEO Kang
to deliver it to him?</i></font>

79
00:08:10,650 --> 00:08:14,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>He could give it to CEO Eun for me.</i></font>

80
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:17,290
<font color=#FFFF00>In the end,
I couldn't give him my drawing.</font>

81
00:08:20,420 --> 00:08:23,660
<font color=#FFFF00>The woman he's seeing...</font>

82
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:28,890
<font color=#FFFF00>is a professional curator
who takes care of real art.</font>

83
00:08:28,890 --> 00:08:30,620
<font color=#FFFF00>But as for me...</font>

84
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,030
<font color=#FFFF00>The drawing I drew...</font>

85
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:38,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it. You can't even drink.</font>

86
00:08:40,910 --> 00:08:43,280
<font color=#FFFF00>But I don't hate that woman.</font>

87
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:49,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Thanks to her,
I got to go on a short date with him.</font>

88
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:56,080
<font color=#FFFF00>I... I was really nervous and excited.</font>

89
00:08:58,740 --> 00:09:01,520
<font color=#FFFF00>- Pardon?
- Thank you for your help.</font>

90
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:03,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh.</font>

91
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey.</font>

92
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:18,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Bad boys are not in style anymore.
Stop being tacky...</font>

93
00:09:18,010 --> 00:09:22,140
<font color=#FFFF00>He's not a bad person! He's warm.</font>

94
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:25,710
<font color=#FFFF00>If a guy mistreats you nine times
but is nice to you once, you're happy.</font>

95
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:30,010
<font color=#FFFF00>If a guy's good to you nine times,
but treats you badly once, he changed.</font>

96
00:09:30,010 --> 00:09:32,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Why can't women do the calculations?</font>

97
00:09:32,470 --> 00:09:36,900
<font color=#FFFF00>If they're good to you nine times
or once, it's so obvious...</font>

98
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:39,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you all that stupid?</font>

99
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:43,810
<font color=#FFFF00>You're right. I'm stupid.</font>

100
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:47,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Even though I know I have no chance</font>

101
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,980
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't help but to look at him.</font>

102
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:52,920
<font color=#FFFF00>The more I look at him,
the more miserable I get...</font>

103
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:55,710
<font color=#FFFF00>but I can't seem to stop.</font>

104
00:09:55,710 --> 00:09:58,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Then tell him! Tell him you like him.</font>

105
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:01,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Then I'll never see him again.</font>

106
00:10:01,370 --> 00:10:04,130
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think I can live
if I can't see him again.</font>

107
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:09,520
<font color=#FFFF00>This is nothing more
than a one-sided love...</font>

108
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you going overboard?</font>

109
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:20,600
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[CEO KANG WOO IL]</i></font>

110
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:24,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, CEO. Right now?</font>

111
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:30,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, okay. I'll be there soon.</font>

112
00:10:30,490 --> 00:10:32,820
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes.
- Hey!</font>

113
00:10:32,820 --> 00:10:36,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Who would call you back
to work at a time like this?</font>

114
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:39,340
<font color=#FFFF00>- What the heck is that?
- It's not him.</font>

115
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:44,440
<font color=#FFFF00>What? You just said "CEO."
You're dumber than I thought!</font>

116
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:50,650
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry. I'll pay for the drinks, okay?</font>

117
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:53,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey. Hey, Chae Ji Hye!</font>

118
00:10:54,730 --> 00:10:56,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't go.</font>

119
00:10:56,890 --> 00:11:01,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Thanks for listening.
I'm glad I have someone to vent to.</font>

120
00:11:01,740 --> 00:11:03,200
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

121
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:33,200
<font color=#FFFF00>You could have looked at her, just once.</font>

122
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:38,750
<font color=#FFFF00>You could have
listened to her, just once.</font>

123
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:43,220
<font color=#FFFF00>She was always
earnestly looking at you...</font>

124
00:11:43,890 --> 00:11:47,050
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you disregard her so brutally?</font>

125
00:11:52,290 --> 00:11:54,280
<font color=#FFFF00>More than anyone else...</font>

126
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:57,960
<font color=#FFFF00>you hurt her the most.</font>

127
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:00,210
<font color=#FFFF00>More than anyone else...</font>

128
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:03,250
<font color=#FFFF00>you are responsible.</font>

129
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:05,520
<font color=#FFFF00>But...</font>

130
00:12:06,410 --> 00:12:09,280
<font color=#FFFF00>you want to be by her sister's side?</font>

131
00:12:19,890 --> 00:12:21,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Reporter Woo...</font>

132
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:29,860
<font color=#FFFF00>worked really hard by himself
to expose the truth three years ago.</font>

133
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:32,470
<font color=#FFFF00>But he was stopped near the end</font>

134
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:36,120
<font color=#FFFF00>and he was even fired
by the publishing company.</font>

135
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:40,280
<font color=#FFFF00>But he never told me about this.</font>

136
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:42,690
<font color=#FFFF00>I think he wanted to...</font>

137
00:12:43,350 --> 00:12:46,340
<font color=#FFFF00>respect Secretary Chae.</font>

138
00:12:46,340 --> 00:12:49,530
<font color=#FFFF00>She would have wanted
to keep it a secret.</font>

139
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Then...</font>

140
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:56,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hye...</font>

141
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:04,720
<font color=#FFFF00>wasn't miserable because
she was rejected by CEO Kang.</font>

142
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:10,070
<font color=#FFFF00>It was because...</font>

143
00:13:10,070 --> 00:13:12,620
<font color=#FFFF00>she couldn't face you again.</font>

144
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:20,690
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess the misery of not
being able to take it all back...</font>

145
00:13:20,690 --> 00:13:22,820
<font color=#FFFF00>was what pushed her over the edge.</font>

146
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:34,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Please.</font>

147
00:13:36,810 --> 00:13:41,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Please... pick up.</font>

148
00:13:41,010 --> 00:13:47,630
<font color=#FFFF00><i>The number is unavailable.
Please leave a message after the tone...</i></font>

149
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:52,000
<font color=#FFFF00>CEO... CEO Eun.</font>

150
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:54,540
<font color=#FFFF00>The intended recipient
of Ji Hye's drawing...</font>

151
00:15:56,930 --> 00:16:01,770
<font color=#FFFF00>was not CEO Kang, but you.</font>

152
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:14,460
<font color=#FFFF00>- What are you drawing?
- Um...</font>

153
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:18,750
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a view that someone
is always looking at.</font>

154
00:16:20,950 --> 00:16:25,590
<font color=#FFFF00><i>I thought there were always
a lot of people around CEO Kang.</i></font>

155
00:16:26,450 --> 00:16:31,940
<font color=#FFFF00><i>I thought that was why she drew
a picture of many people in a building.</i></font>

156
00:16:31,940 --> 00:16:34,010
<font color=#FFFF00><i>But it wasn't true...</i></font>

157
00:16:37,870 --> 00:16:39,490
<font color=#FFFF00>CEO Eun.</font>

158
00:17:52,990 --> 00:17:54,760
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

159
00:17:56,050 --> 00:18:00,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, I'm just...</font>

160
00:18:00,170 --> 00:18:04,290
<font color=#FFFF00>I realized, on your window sill...</font>

161
00:18:04,290 --> 00:18:06,910
<font color=#FFFF00>there's no dust. It's clean.</font>

162
00:18:06,910 --> 00:18:11,150
<font color=#FFFF00>I do the cleaning.
You don't have to worry about that.</font>

163
00:18:11,150 --> 00:18:13,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I apologize.</font>

164
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:17,870
<font color=#FFFF00>The view that you always
admire outside your window.</font>

165
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:25,660
<font color=#FFFF00>The flower shop and bakery
on the first floor...</font>

166
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:29,170
<font color=#FFFF00>A cafe on the second floor...</font>

167
00:19:29,170 --> 00:19:31,340
<font color=#FFFF00>And a hair salon on the third floor.</font>

168
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:33,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that right?</font>

169
00:19:38,190 --> 00:19:40,890
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess...</font>

170
00:19:40,890 --> 00:19:44,370
<font color=#FFFF00>she wanted to fill that
concrete building with people.</font>

171
00:19:46,610 --> 00:19:50,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Because you're always alone...</font>

172
00:19:50,260 --> 00:19:55,520
<font color=#FFFF00>I think she wanted
warm people to be by your side.</font>

173
00:20:02,870 --> 00:20:04,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Here.</font>

174
00:20:08,250 --> 00:20:10,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Take it.</font>

175
00:20:21,930 --> 00:20:26,550
<font color=#FFFF00>The picture finally found
its rightful owner.</font>

176
00:22:34,340 --> 00:22:36,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you looking at me like that?</font>

177
00:22:37,090 --> 00:22:41,890
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it's just... that you look different.</font>

178
00:22:42,770 --> 00:22:46,940
<font color=#FFFF00>I've never seen you
so laid back, even at home.</font>

179
00:22:47,670 --> 00:22:49,620
<font color=#FFFF00>It wakes you up, doesn't it?</font>

180
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:52,420
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

181
00:22:53,380 --> 00:22:55,310
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the real me.</font>

182
00:22:56,490 --> 00:23:00,450
<font color=#FFFF00>No, you look comfortable.</font>

183
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:03,610
<font color=#FFFF00>I am.</font>

184
00:23:05,490 --> 00:23:08,950
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't have to dress up
because I'm always at home.</font>

185
00:23:08,950 --> 00:23:11,930
<font color=#FFFF00>And I don't have to say
what I don't want to say.</font>

186
00:23:11,930 --> 00:23:16,180
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't have to strain myself because
of what others might think either.</font>

187
00:23:17,690 --> 00:23:20,320
<font color=#FFFF00>You're always home?</font>

188
00:23:21,050 --> 00:23:23,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom and Dad want me
to stay home for the time being.</font>

189
00:23:24,770 --> 00:23:28,620
<font color=#FFFF00>- They must be embarrassed of me.
- Hey, no way.</font>

190
00:23:28,620 --> 00:23:29,910
<font color=#FFFF00>They're worried...</font>

191
00:23:29,910 --> 00:23:34,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, I sneaked out just now,
so I have to go back soon.</font>

192
00:23:36,170 --> 00:23:38,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you call me here?</font>

193
00:23:44,090 --> 00:23:48,120
<font color=#FFFF00>I... was worried about you.</font>

194
00:23:49,140 --> 00:23:52,710
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't think you
were lacking in any way.</font>

195
00:23:54,490 --> 00:23:58,280
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought you were someone
who didn't need my help.</font>

196
00:23:59,570 --> 00:24:04,120
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why when you did anything
for me, I took it for granted...</font>

197
00:24:05,580 --> 00:24:07,280
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

