00:42:33,900 --> 00:42:37,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Marry Hwan Ki?</font>

398
00:42:39,260 --> 00:42:41,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Just the thought makes me happy.</font>

399
00:42:41,160 --> 00:42:43,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Excuse me, but...</font>

400
00:42:43,500 --> 00:42:48,210
<font color=#FFFF00>But what can I say?
I wouldn't like my future father-in-law.</font>

401
00:42:49,260 --> 00:42:51,030
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

402
00:42:51,560 --> 00:42:55,180
<font color=#FFFF00>I like how careful Hwan Ki is.</font>

403
00:42:55,180 --> 00:42:59,760
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a bit slow,
but he's considerate of others.</font>

404
00:42:59,760 --> 00:43:01,840
<font color=#FFFF00>That's just because...</font>

405
00:43:02,340 --> 00:43:04,930
<font color=#FFFF00>But you're very different from him.</font>

406
00:43:04,930 --> 00:43:08,390
<font color=#FFFF00>You're more vigorous and impatient
with an impelling drive.</font>

407
00:43:08,980 --> 00:43:12,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Since I'm more like that,
I wouldn't like someone similar.</font>

408
00:43:16,560 --> 00:43:21,470
<font color=#FFFF00>I appreciate you thinking highly of me
and asking me out here.</font>

409
00:43:21,470 --> 00:43:25,930
<font color=#FFFF00>But I thought you'd talk to him first.</font>

410
00:43:25,930 --> 00:43:28,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Seeing you push forward this urgently...</font>

411
00:43:28,630 --> 00:43:31,640
<font color=#FFFF00>I assume you already looked into me.</font>

412
00:43:31,640 --> 00:43:33,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

413
00:43:33,930 --> 00:43:37,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Since we're talking about it,
I'll be upfront.</font>

414
00:43:37,130 --> 00:43:39,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Can we not live with you guys
after we get married?</font>

415
00:43:39,630 --> 00:43:43,150
<font color=#FFFF00>We will come over
on major holidays and such.</font>

416
00:43:43,150 --> 00:43:45,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Does your family hold memorial
services for your ancestors?</font>

417
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:47,950
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not good at making such dishes.</font>

418
00:43:48,760 --> 00:43:50,670
<font color=#FFFF00>I admit that I was too hasty.</font>

419
00:43:58,260 --> 00:44:00,570
<font color=#FFFF00>I was too rude, wasn't I?</font>

420
00:44:00,570 --> 00:44:02,770
<font color=#FFFF00>But I really don't think this is the way.</font>

421
00:44:02,770 --> 00:44:05,930
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry I made you uncomfortable.</font>

422
00:44:07,510 --> 00:44:10,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Is this the start of my sad love story</font>

423
00:44:10,860 --> 00:44:13,540
<font color=#FFFF00>where I go against
my family's wishes?</font>

424
00:44:40,060 --> 00:44:42,210
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[NEW YORK BARBER]</i></font>

425
00:44:42,270 --> 00:44:43,850
<font color=#FFFF00>What's all that?</font>

426
00:44:44,700 --> 00:44:46,910
<font color=#FFFF00>We have to keep this place alive.</font>

427
00:44:46,910 --> 00:44:49,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Actually, I have
experience in promotions.</font>

428
00:44:51,260 --> 00:44:55,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Maybe it's time to get out
of this tiny barbershop.</font>

429
00:44:58,060 --> 00:45:00,560
<font color=#FFFF00>You've also felt suffocated.</font>

430
00:45:00,560 --> 00:45:03,670
<font color=#FFFF00>This is where your whole
life story is written.</font>

431
00:45:04,260 --> 00:45:09,610
<font color=#FFFF00>We should protect our memories
with Mom and my sister.</font>

432
00:45:15,260 --> 00:45:17,380
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[NEW YORK BARBER]
[30 YEARS OF TRADITION]</i></font>

433
00:45:17,520 --> 00:45:20,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, I'm from New York Barber.</font>

434
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:22,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello. Thank you.</font>

435
00:45:22,760 --> 00:45:24,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello. Please take this.</font>

436
00:45:24,790 --> 00:45:26,450
<font color=#FFFF00>This is New York Barber.</font>

437
00:45:26,450 --> 00:45:28,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Please come.</font>

438
00:45:28,100 --> 00:45:29,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

439
00:45:44,730 --> 00:45:46,660
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aw, so cute.
- How cute.</font>

440
00:45:47,770 --> 00:45:49,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Boss?</font>

441
00:45:51,220 --> 00:45:53,670
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aw, so cute.
- How cute.</font>

442
00:45:55,210 --> 00:45:56,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Boss?</font>

443
00:46:01,100 --> 00:46:02,940
<font color=#FFFF00>What is he thinking?</font>

444
00:46:15,290 --> 00:46:17,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Please leave.</font>

445
00:46:17,080 --> 00:46:19,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't do that.</font>

446
00:46:26,670 --> 00:46:28,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Boss.</font>

447
00:46:32,990 --> 00:46:35,000
<font color=#FFFF00>What? You're not Boss?</font>

448
00:46:35,000 --> 00:46:37,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you Jang Se Jong then?</font>

449
00:46:37,860 --> 00:46:41,980
<font color=#FFFF00>No way. You're Boss. Let me see then.</font>

450
00:46:52,090 --> 00:46:53,550
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

451
00:46:54,320 --> 00:46:57,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Seeing how cute he is and all...
is it really Jang Se Jong?</font>

452
00:46:58,290 --> 00:47:01,110
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Fine, I'm Jang Se Jong today.</i></font>

453
00:47:01,110 --> 00:47:05,640
<font color=#FFFF00><i>In order to be with you,
I can lose myself and be anybody else.</i></font>

454
00:47:07,290 --> 00:47:08,950
<font color=#FFFF00>So cute.</font>

455
00:47:11,990 --> 00:47:13,690
<font color=#FFFF00>So cute!</font>

456
00:47:13,690 --> 00:47:15,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Include this sign please.</font>

457
00:47:15,190 --> 00:47:17,620
<font color=#FFFF00>It's New York Barber, people!</font>

458
00:47:17,620 --> 00:47:19,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Please come by!</font>

459
00:47:32,290 --> 00:47:33,690
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Honestly...</i></font>

460
00:47:33,690 --> 00:47:36,040
<font color=#FFFF00><i>I'm getting...</i></font>

461
00:47:36,040 --> 00:47:38,680
<font color=#FFFF00><i>too old for this.</i></font>

462
00:47:41,890 --> 00:47:44,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Here, drink this.</font>

463
00:47:44,280 --> 00:47:46,110
<font color=#FFFF00>"Drink this"?</font>

464
00:47:46,110 --> 00:47:49,360
<font color=#FFFF00>You're Jang Se Jong.
I can't talk to you that way?</font>

465
00:47:51,540 --> 00:47:54,120
<font color=#FFFF00>That's enough, Boss.</font>

466
00:47:54,120 --> 00:47:57,350
<font color=#FFFF00>It must be hard, so take it off, okay?</font>

467
00:48:03,390 --> 00:48:05,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Seriously, hold still.</font>

468
00:48:05,740 --> 00:48:09,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Now reveal yourself!</font>

469
00:48:09,110 --> 00:48:10,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Seriously.</font>

470
00:48:14,790 --> 00:48:18,680
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?
Let me go, Boss.</font>

471
00:48:19,390 --> 00:48:21,380
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

472
00:48:22,690 --> 00:48:28,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you just think this isn't me?</font>

473
00:48:30,990 --> 00:48:37,500
<font color=#FFFF00>I just want to see your face once.</font>

474
00:48:39,200 --> 00:48:44,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Can I see your face
even if it's like this?</font>

475
00:48:45,940 --> 00:48:49,230
<font color=#FFFF00>I've missed you so much.</font>

476
00:48:59,590 --> 00:49:04,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Mommy, if a bear and
a human fall in love...</font>

477
00:49:04,550 --> 00:49:07,700
<font color=#FFFF00>will Dangun be born?
(FOUNDER OF GOJEOSEON, "SON OF A BEAR")</font>

478
00:49:07,700 --> 00:49:08,960
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you saying?</font>

479
00:49:08,960 --> 00:49:10,520
<font color=#FFFF00>No Ah, let's go.</font>

480
00:49:28,990 --> 00:49:30,960
<font color=#FFFF00>After this, just go.</font>

481
00:49:30,960 --> 00:49:32,990
<font color=#FFFF00>You said you missed me.</font>

482
00:49:32,990 --> 00:49:35,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Missing you is one thing.</font>

483
00:49:35,520 --> 00:49:37,790
<font color=#FFFF00>But the fact we can't be together
is an entirely different matter.</font>

484
00:49:39,290 --> 00:49:41,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Here. Since I have a very low
budget for this promotion</font>

485
00:49:41,940 --> 00:49:44,440
<font color=#FFFF00>this is all I can afford.</font>

486
00:49:44,440 --> 00:49:47,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you for coming though.</font>

487
00:49:50,590 --> 00:49:52,910
<font color=#FFFF00>No need to thank me.</font>

488
00:49:54,290 --> 00:50:00,470
<font color=#FFFF00>It was my father who made
things difficult for the barbershop.</font>

489
00:50:00,470 --> 00:50:05,000
<font color=#FFFF00>What? How could he?</font>

490
00:50:05,000 --> 00:50:07,290
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

491
00:50:07,290 --> 00:50:11,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Now there is one more
reason it can't be me.</font>

492
00:50:13,290 --> 00:50:15,530
<font color=#FFFF00>But I still came.</font>

493
00:50:15,530 --> 00:50:21,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if I shouldn't,
I decided to do it anyway.</font>

494
00:50:22,690 --> 00:50:27,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you come this way, I can't...</font>

495
00:50:28,590 --> 00:50:32,040
<font color=#FFFF00>All this time, it was you who came to me.</font>

496
00:50:32,040 --> 00:50:35,420
<font color=#FFFF00>You believed in me
without knowing what I was up to.</font>

497
00:50:35,420 --> 00:50:39,530
<font color=#FFFF00>After you learned the truth,
you easily forgave me.</font>

498
00:50:41,370 --> 00:50:45,660
<font color=#FFFF00>It's okay to lock yourself in.</font>

499
00:50:45,980 --> 00:50:49,620
<font color=#FFFF00>All the things you did for me,
such as knocking on my door...</font>

500
00:50:49,620 --> 00:50:56,280
<font color=#FFFF00>making sure I was okay,
and taking me out of my room.</font>

501
00:50:57,510 --> 00:50:59,890
<font color=#FFFF00>I will do all that from now on.</font>

502
00:51:05,290 --> 00:51:08,960
<font color=#FFFF00>How am I supposed to face my late sister?</font>

503
00:51:09,590 --> 00:51:10,880
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't do that.</font>

504
00:51:10,880 --> 00:51:13,890
<font color=#FFFF00>I will do what you can't do.</font>

505
00:51:13,890 --> 00:51:17,720
<font color=#FFFF00>I will be indecent enough to stay
with you when you tell me not to.</font>

506
00:51:17,720 --> 00:51:19,200
<font color=#FFFF00>I will do it all.</font>

507
00:51:20,940 --> 00:51:23,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you do all that, I still can't.</font>

508
00:51:24,690 --> 00:51:29,010
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the job of the special forces
to make the impossible possible.</font>

509
00:51:29,010 --> 00:51:30,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Special forces.</font>

510
00:51:32,590 --> 00:51:35,790
<font color=#FFFF00>So let me help with the barbershop, okay?</font>

511
00:51:35,790 --> 00:51:38,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Because my father is responsible. Okay?</font>

512
00:51:41,700 --> 00:51:43,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Please let me do it.</font>

513
00:51:44,130 --> 00:51:46,950
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know.</font>

514
00:52:05,990 --> 00:52:09,120
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the same as what
happened three years ago.</font>

515
00:52:17,490 --> 00:52:21,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you scream,
people don't hear you out.</font>

516
00:52:21,840 --> 00:52:24,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Something is different now.</font>

517
00:52:24,410 --> 00:52:25,980
<font color=#FFFF00>What is?</font>

518
00:52:25,980 --> 00:52:28,580
<font color=#FFFF00>You're not alone now.</font>

519
00:52:28,580 --> 00:52:31,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, you're so cheesy now.</font>

520
00:52:31,050 --> 00:52:33,360
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm about to have one more reason
why you shouldn't be...</font>

521
00:52:33,360 --> 00:52:35,300
<font color=#FFFF00>I wasn't talking about me.</font>

522
00:53:00,700 --> 00:53:02,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

523
00:53:02,120 --> 00:53:05,760
<font color=#FFFF00>I knew you'd do promotions
at this elementary level.</font>

524
00:53:05,760 --> 00:53:09,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you dare tell people
you work at Silent Monster!</font>

525
00:53:09,010 --> 00:53:10,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Sun Bong.</font>

526
00:53:10,670 --> 00:53:13,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Agreed. You have a lot to learn.</font>

527
00:53:13,270 --> 00:53:14,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Who said you could quit?</font>

528
00:53:15,530 --> 00:53:16,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Yoo Hee.</font>

529
00:53:16,700 --> 00:53:19,560
<font color=#FFFF00>You should've called me about this.</font>

530
00:53:20,290 --> 00:53:23,170
<font color=#FFFF00>We all came to help, Ro Woon.</font>

531
00:53:27,080 --> 00:53:31,370
<font color=#FFFF00>You all seriously... thank you all.</font>

532
00:53:41,460 --> 00:53:45,620
<font color=#FFFF00><i>As you already know,
going to a hair salon is trendy.</i></font>

533
00:53:45,840 --> 00:53:50,510
<font color=#FFFF00><i>If we beg you to come to
an almost-forgotten barbershop...</i></font>

534
00:53:50,510 --> 00:53:52,290
<font color=#FFFF00><i>we will only sound pathetic.</i></font>

535
00:53:52,290 --> 00:53:53,780
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Then what?</i></font>

536
00:53:53,780 --> 00:53:56,530
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Rather than complaining about
the changes of the world...</i></font>

537
00:53:56,530 --> 00:54:00,170
<font color=#FFFF00><i>it's easier, faster, and
more effective to change myself.</i></font>

538
00:54:05,010 --> 00:54:06,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you like red ginseng?</font>

539
00:54:06,700 --> 00:54:08,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Take one.</font>

540
00:54:08,140 --> 00:54:11,890
<font color=#FFFF00>And then can you fill out this survey?</font>

541
00:54:11,890 --> 00:54:13,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, could you fill out this survey?</font>

542
00:54:13,960 --> 00:54:16,470
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hello.
- Hello.</font>

543
00:54:16,470 --> 00:54:18,750
<font color=#FFFF00>- Take this red ginseng.
- Can you take this survey?</font>

544
00:54:18,750 --> 00:54:20,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Feel free to answer the questions.</font>

545
00:54:20,670 --> 00:54:23,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Take this red ginseng as a reward.</font>

546
00:54:23,660 --> 00:54:25,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Take one survey sheet.</font>

547
00:54:25,070 --> 00:54:28,020
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yoo Hee, you take one, too.
- One for me?</font>

548
00:54:32,590 --> 00:54:36,560
<font color=#FFFF00><i>We have do thorough market
research first for renovation.</i></font>

549
00:55:04,870 --> 00:55:06,110
<font color=#FFFF00>You look like an actor.</font>

550
00:55:14,050 --> 00:55:16,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Wow, you look cool.</font>

551
00:55:16,020 --> 00:55:19,980
<font color=#FFFF00>It looks good on you.
It makes you look 10 years younger.</font>

552
00:55:24,290 --> 00:55:26,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you my dad?</font>

553
00:55:26,070 --> 00:55:29,300
<font color=#FFFF00>You look cool. You look so different.</font>

554
00:55:29,300 --> 00:55:32,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Why don't you replace
the towels altogether?</font>

555
00:55:32,330 --> 00:55:34,740
<font color=#FFFF00>To match the theme of the interior
and even the sign outside.</font>

556
00:55:34,740 --> 00:55:38,170
<font color=#FFFF00>You can also change the name
of the shop to match the theme.</font>

557
00:55:38,170 --> 00:55:42,030
<font color=#FFFF00>It would be nice to change
the floor, ceiling, and wall this way.</font>

558
00:55:42,030 --> 00:55:47,760
<font color=#FFFF00>I... don't know how to
thank you for all this.</font>

559
00:55:48,350 --> 00:55:53,940
<font color=#FFFF00>But I'm uncomfortable
with this whole idea.</font>

560
00:55:54,810 --> 00:55:57,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Change is the only way to survive.</font>

561
00:55:57,120 --> 00:55:59,140
<font color=#FFFF00>If I want to change everything</font>

562
00:55:59,140 --> 00:56:02,190
<font color=#FFFF00>what's the point of
staying at that location?</font>

563
00:56:02,190 --> 00:56:07,370
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry that you
put a lot of work into this.</font>

564
00:56:07,370 --> 00:56:09,300
<font color=#FFFF00>- It's okay.
- Not at all.</font>

565
00:56:09,300 --> 00:56:12,220
<font color=#FFFF00>- You're entitled to feel that way.
- Not at all, sir.</font>

566
00:56:14,580 --> 00:56:16,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad...</font>

567
00:56:31,290 --> 00:56:35,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Then... I will go home first.</font>

568
00:56:35,490 --> 00:56:37,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Please get home safely.</font>

569
00:56:42,590 --> 00:56:47,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Why doesn't he want to
come out of his comfort zone?</font>

570
00:56:47,710 --> 00:56:52,350
<font color=#FFFF00>It was our fault for pushing him to
change without asking him first.</font>

571
00:56:52,350 --> 00:56:55,620
<font color=#FFFF00>We have to find a way to get through
to him that won't change him.</font>

572
00:56:58,330 --> 00:56:59,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Does such a thing exist?</font>

573
00:57:01,290 --> 00:57:03,730
<font color=#FFFF00>I only heard someone say that.</font>

574
00:57:05,590 --> 00:57:08,860
<font color=#FFFF00>There has to be a way of
communicating that works for you.</font>

575
00:57:08,860 --> 00:57:11,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Try to find it.</font>

576
00:57:11,260 --> 00:57:12,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't try to change.</font>

577
00:57:22,490 --> 00:57:26,020
<font color=#FFFF00>I will find a way, so don't worry.</font>

578
00:57:26,020 --> 00:57:27,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Go home.</font>

579
00:57:28,590 --> 00:57:31,140
<font color=#FFFF00>- I will go home then.
- Go ahead.</font>

580
00:57:46,910 --> 00:57:48,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Suk Joon?</font>

581
00:57:49,540 --> 00:57:51,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Please do me this favor.</font>

582
00:57:55,290 --> 00:57:58,400
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a very famous anchor...</font>

583
00:57:58,400 --> 00:58:01,990
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't guarantee if he'll do it or not.</font>

584
00:58:01,990 --> 00:58:04,250
<font color=#FFFF00>- You know that, right?
- Sure. Thank you.</font>

585
00:58:04,250 --> 00:58:06,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Just ask him to take
a look at the proposal.</font>

586
00:58:06,550 --> 00:58:07,860
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[NEW YORK BARBER]</i></font>

587
00:58:09,320 --> 00:58:12,390
<font color=#FFFF00>In return, I also have
a favor to ask of you.</font>

588
00:58:12,390 --> 00:58:15,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you pretend to be
my boyfriend just once?</font>

589
00:58:15,220 --> 00:58:16,740
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

590
00:58:16,740 --> 00:58:19,960
<font color=#FFFF00>You know he's my first crush
from my church, right?</font>

591
00:58:20,550 --> 00:58:22,940
<font color=#FFFF00>I was a kid at that time who wore braces.</font>

592
00:58:22,940 --> 00:58:26,100
<font color=#FFFF00>I want to show him
that I'm totally different now.</font>

593
00:58:27,290 --> 00:58:29,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Of all people, why me?</font>

594
00:58:29,330 --> 00:58:32,030
<font color=#FFFF00>I played a rude bride-to-be
